{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"23e31faf51","title":"张春桥姚文元与广播事业局《毛泽东思想战斗团》的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7f4cba13c0","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":11,"articleId":"23e31faf51","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"张春桥","id":"471a503675","type":"人物"},{"name":"姚文元","id":"92a8a42842","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"45f848c5df","name":"姚文元"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[{"id":"bd4f970475","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"《毛泽东思想的光辉照耀着中央广播事业局――毛主席以及中央首长对中央广播事业局无产阶级文化大革命的历次指示汇编（1966年7月－1968年6月）》（中央广播事业局《无产阶级革命派联合总部》，一九六八年七月）"}],"contents":[{"id":"5e2e809494","type":"title","text":"张春桥姚文元与广播事业局《毛泽东思想战斗团》的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d3bc031f04","type":"paragraph","text":"〖按：一九六六年十月十八日，《毛泽东思想战斗团》从资产阶级反动路线的白色恐怖中冲杀出来，大造梅益、丁莱夫等一小撮走资派的反。丁莱夫为了维持梅丁王朝的反动统治，扑灭革命的烈火，操纵《誓死纵队》和《红色造反团》，围剿革命派。在我们斗争最艰苦，最激烈的时刻，十二月十一日下午，毛主席司令部派张春桥、姚文元同志来我局，接见了《毛泽东思想战斗团》的十五名代表。张春桥、姚文元同志和代表们亲切交谈了三个多小时，对《毛泽东思想战斗团》的革命行动表示支持。下面是这次接见的谈话纪要。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7f2c2fbca0","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我们想了解一下情况，找你们党委谈过。我们知道你们有好几个群众组织，基本上有三个，我们都想谈一下，先和你们谈。我们了解过一些情况，但不很多。你们各派都写过信。你们看有什么问题，有什么困难，打算怎么做，或者你们认为需要的，我们都想了解。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf964a1611","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：就这样吧，你们说，我们听。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"170190dc96","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：要不要先挨个介绍一下？","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c4a6d96684","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：介绍一下吧，你们哪几个是主要负责的？","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cae1828a59","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们有没有团委呀？","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"001debba2f","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，我们只有联络员。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c467662a5d","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报丁莱夫的“七 · 二九”黑报告，当谈到丁莱夫说群众批评他是“鸡蛋里头挑骨头” 时）","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4f39da87fd","type":"paragraph","text":"张：这是谁说的？丁莱夫？","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"480daa30ab","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：对。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a86f439298","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报丁莱夫搞假选举阴谋）","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"36d9895788","type":"paragraph","text":"张：那你们局里现在还没有选举文革委员会？","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9e3640aa53","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，还是旧文革领导。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ed5f3977dd","type":"paragraph","text":"张：是指定的，还是选举的？","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f5af1acf1b","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：选举的，但实际上是指定的，基本上是局党委和各大口负责人。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3572b93a60","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报丁莱夫在广播学院事件上，对抗中央文革的罪行。谈到丁说“不能说一千二百人都是右派”时）","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"031b674291","type":"paragraph","text":"张：那时特别对一千二百人讲了话，说你们是受蒙蔽的，包括工作组的大多数，都是好的。我们再三讲。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d0263338bc","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：他根本没有传达这些。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"283115cc81","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报局文革迫害鲁迅的儿子周海婴。当谈到有人问周海婴去南方干什么时）","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6961b70aa0","type":"paragraph","text":"张：是不是丁莱夫直接问的？","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1febedac1","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表介绍情况）","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8680ddabd","type":"paragraph","text":"张：丁莱夫说他不知道周海婴是中央文革派去的。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"82b33abd70","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：他们对周海婴采取了什么行动？","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"91d45bfd8e","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：准备开斗争会，会议程序，口号都拟好了。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f4c7d58f6c","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报斗争梅益情况）","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"46005cc27f","type":"paragraph","text":"张：梅益开了几天会？","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee6f23bef3","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：四天。后转入小会。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb973d60ea","type":"paragraph","text":"张：有材料可以给我们看，因为情况很多，先谈当前情况。政训队呀，软禁室呀，都是怎么回事？都解决了没有？现在还存在吗？","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67129876c8","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表介绍政训队情况）","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6cdcf8b048","type":"paragraph","text":"张：政训队有多少人？","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e498084476","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：九十多个。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1fb00d63d6","type":"paragraph","text":"张：黑帮占多少？","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c53bed400","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：六十三个。群众十八个。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a09dc80aec","type":"paragraph","text":"张：政训队还存在吗？黑帮是怎么定的？这有六十多人，还有十八个人，还有工作人员，三种人。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"22a71133f4","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：对。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bf49e96586","type":"paragraph","text":"代表（受资产阶级反动路线迫害，被送进政训队的王××同志）：说我们是中间人物。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"69ce15c5a2","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：中间人物？（笑）","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"95a803e6f6","type":"paragraph","text":"张：中间人物和黑帮一样待遇吗？","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a0ca22e6d","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：政治待遇上基本一样。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"afa10de891","type":"paragraph","text":"张：和工作人员呢？","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd1f47c4b7","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：不一样。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e90774dfb3","type":"paragraph","text":"张：现在这样的还有多少人？最多的时候多少人？","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80c898da62","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：十八个人。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7cd048a98e","type":"paragraph","text":"张：软禁室怎么样？","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"06636dfdd9","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表介绍软禁室情况，谈到走资派，原中控室主任景润身时）","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f1d4a67043","type":"paragraph","text":"张：他真有本领吗？技术上怎么样？","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e80f2646e4","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：他根本不怎么样。","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40f175318c","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你就讲讲软禁室内幕。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dad458387d","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：软禁室有多少人？","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f1098cee6a","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：八个人。","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b4f2e968f7","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：控制室一共多少人？","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"93911cd7c6","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：××××人。","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c7773ee1c","type":"paragraph","text":"张：现在还禁闭着吗？","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6218e6efc","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，但没有公开平反。","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7ecc1eb5a4","type":"paragraph","text":"张：多久的时间？","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7654e69695","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：最早是八月底去的。","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"14093e9872","type":"paragraph","text":"张：其他单位还有没有软禁室？","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"46920131a9","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：大楼里只有一个。","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8dc70d4b05","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报有一次毛主席接见红卫兵时，电视中出现丁莱夫，《誓死纵队》一些队员欢呼）","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"903ab5e861","type":"paragraph","text":"张：哪一次接见？","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"163e32f295","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：大概第六次。","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c07022088f","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报当前运动的阻力和几个组织的情况）","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"114ee6b6b2","type":"paragraph","text":"张：誓死队有多少人？","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc1248417c","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：他们说五百。","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ff2c36884e","type":"paragraph","text":"张：丁莱夫找过你们这些人开过会吗？","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5222b79498","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：没有，他不敢。","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a69d3d2fb4","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报我局资产阶级反动路线的执行者，妄图用所谓“党纪”来镇压造反派。胡说什么“党员对党组织有意见，只有按组织系统向上一级反映，不能公开贴大字报。”代表批驳了这种谬论，并请示首长应该怎样回答这个问题。）","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c372602c53","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你刚才已经答复了嘛！这样答复就可以。如果出了修正主义，包括党中央出了修正主义，就造他的反，不然，就要陷于苏联赫鲁晓夫式的统治。向上级控告？赫鲁晓夫的上级是谁呀？（众笑。）","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c19c867a6f","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报传达室刚刚摘掉刘少奇的题词）","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7ce7255675","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：他们想毁灭罪证嘛！专家接待室是否还挂着？","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7980a3d80","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：不知道。","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4c5531a805","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们大楼有多少人？","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cffdbddf85","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：×××人。","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b155fe6887","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报政治情况）","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e8fe063ff","type":"paragraph","text":"张：政治部有多少人？你们战斗团占多少？","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6308c6421","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：政治部×××人，我们只有一人。","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ba0888dc1","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们开会在剧场开？能容纳多少人？","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e3e5b39d7","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：××××人。","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8a158669b0","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报\"一一 · 二\"事件，《誓死纵队》要首长上×楼政治部时）","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c82bb51b4b","type":"paragraph","text":"张：那天非让我们到×楼去不可，气势汹汹。那天我们家里有事，不然就去了。","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb6ff86458","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：后来我们要去，他们又不让去了。","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ca09d14e14","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报《誓死纵队》派人到国务院告张春桥，姚文元同志的状）","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b38b8668e5","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我知道。他们要找我辩论，我没理他们。","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a3627b42b4","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报“一一·四”事件）","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb920cbdf2","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我知道。","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"510c55e22f","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表汇报“一二·九”大阴谋。）","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f66a296d68","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：可以想一想这个问题嘛！","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"51709a6cbd","type":"paragraph","text":"（首长上车时，代表说：“欢迎首长常来”。）","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67cdcd2166","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：革命还要靠自己嘛！","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"23e31faf51","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}